instruction: Create a shopping list for a vegan dinner for two.
output:
Couscous: 1 cup
Vegetables (carrots, zucchini, mushrooms, bell peppers): 2-3 cups
Olive oil: 3-4 tablespoons
Garlic: 3-4 cloves
Tomato sauce: 1 can
Chickpeas: 1 can
Vegan cheese: 1 block
Salt and pepper: to taste
Basil: 1/4 cup
Broccoli: 1-2 cups
Cherry tomatoes: 1-2 cups
Lentils: 1 cup
Onion: 1/2 onion
Balsamic vinegar: 1/4 cup
Avocado: 1-2 avocados
